528
00:44:26,930 --> 00:44:28,198
THANK YOU, JAMES.

529
00:44:30,067 --> 00:44:33,203
I'D LIKE TO ASK YOU SOMETHING.

530
00:44:33,237 --> 00:44:35,472
OKAY, IAN.

531
00:44:35,506 --> 00:44:40,477
WHAT'S IT LIKE WORKING FOR DR. RENQUIST?

532
00:44:40,511 --> 00:44:44,214
WELL, HE'S A WONDERFUL MAN. A WONDERFUL MAN.

533
00:44:46,984 --> 00:44:51,188
JONAS, PLEASE.

534
00:45:23,153 --> 00:45:25,255
PLEASE.

