TERESA, I--

580
00:51:12,803 --> 00:51:15,572
PLEASE. DON'T SAY ANYTHING.

581
00:51:15,605 --> 00:51:17,507
YOU NEED HELP.

582
00:51:17,541 --> 00:51:19,576
THAT'S ALL THERE IS TO SAY.

583
00:51:24,247 --> 00:51:26,483
ALL THESE YEARS,

584
00:51:26,516 --> 00:51:31,354
TREATING PEOPLE.

