00:51:31,388 --> 00:51:33,490
LECTURING OTHER PSYCHIATRISTS

586
00:51:33,523 --> 00:51:36,860
ON HOW TO TREAT PEOPLE.

587
00:51:36,893 --> 00:51:40,297
OH! LOOK AT ME. LOOK AT ME. DID I DO THIS?

588
00:51:40,330 --> 00:51:43,300
IAN, PLEASE STOP.

589
00:51:43,333 --> 00:51:45,936
