THAT'S WHY YOU'RE HERE.

597
00:52:03,620 --> 00:52:05,689
JUST LET THEM HELP YOU.

598
00:52:11,628 --> 00:52:13,563
I WANNA GO HOME.

599
00:52:13,597 --> 00:52:17,634
I DON'T BELONG HERE.

600
00:52:17,667 --> 00:52:22,372
TERESA, I'M SCARED OF THIS PLACE.

601
00:52:22,405 --> 00:52:25,942
IT CAN BE BETTER. I DON'T WANNA BE SICK.

602
00:52:25,976 --> 00:52:28,411
I DON'T WANNA DRINK ANYMORE.

603
00:52:28,445 --> 00:52:30,680
LISTEN TO ME. IT WILL BE BETTER.

604
00:52:30,714 --> 00:52:34,351
GOD, IAN. LISTEN TO YOURSELF.

605
00:52:34,384 --> 00:52:37,787
DO YOU EVEN HEAR WHAT YOU'RE SAYING?

606
00:52:37,821 --> 00:52:41,625
