607
00:52:44,261 --> 00:52:45,762
WE HAVE TO GO.

608
00:52:47,631 --> 00:52:49,666
I DON'T WANNA BE ALONE.

609
00:52:49,699 --> 00:52:51,635
I CAN'T STAND BEING ALONE.

610
00:52:51,668 --> 00:52:53,737
IAN, PLEASE.

611
00:52:53,770 --> 00:52:56,840
FINISH WHAT YOU STARTED.

612
00:52:56,873 --> 00:52:59,809
- PROMISE ME ONE THING. - WHAT?

613
00:52:59,843 --> 00:53:04,915
WILL YOU BE THERE WHEN I GET OUT?

614
00:53:04,948 --> 00:53:06,983
I DON'T KNOW.

615
00:53:07,017 --> 00:53:09,653
WE'LL SEE.

616
00:53:15,592 --> 00:53:17,727
QUITE A PLACE, IAN.

617
00:53:17,761 --> 00:53:19,930
KILLER NURSING STAFF.

618
00:53:19,963 --> 00:53:22,799
JOE, WE HAVE TO GO. IT'S GETTING LATE.

619
00:53:28,672 --> 00:53:31,841
- IS SHE OKAY? - I DON'T KNOW.

620
00:53:33,910 --> 00:53:37,647
LISTEN, I'M REALLY SORRY ABOUT ALL THIS, BUDDY,

621
00:53:37,681 --> 00:53:41,418
