622
00:53:41,451 --> 00:53:45,055
I TOLD HER THAT I THOUGHT YOU COULD SOBER UP FINE BY YOURSELF,

623
00:53:45,088 --> 00:53:47,891
BUT SHE SAID THIS WAS GONNA BE GOOD FOR YOU.

624
00:53:47,924 --> 00:53:50,427
YOU'VE GOTTA GET ME OUT OF HERE.

625
00:53:50,460 --> 00:53:53,697
JOE, YOU GOT TO GET ME THE FUCK OUT OF HERE.

626
00:53:53,730 --> 00:53:56,666
I WILL, I WILL. NO PROBLEM, NO PROBLEM.

627
00:53:58,802 --> 00:54:02,405
HEY, YOU NEED ANYTHING, YOU CALL ME, ALL RIGHT?

628
00:54:03,406 --> 00:54:05,075
TAKE CARE OF TERESA, WILL YOU?

629
00:54:05,108 --> 00:54:07,077
I WILL.

630
00:54:10,947 --> 00:54:13,416
I'LL SEE YA, ALL RIGHT?

631
00:55:10,940 --> 00:55:13,143
WELCOME, IAN.

632
00:55:13,176 --> 00:55:15,445
HOW DO YOU FEEL TODAY?

633
00:55:15,478 --> 00:55:17,781
WELL, LET'S SEE.

634
00:55:17,814 --> 00:55:20,950
ACUTE WITHDRAWAL, AND ASSOCIATED SYMPTOMS

635
00:55:20,984 --> 00:55:24,020
OF DETOXIFICATION SUBSIDED ABOUT A WEEK AGO.

636
00:55:24,054 --> 00:55:26,122
THE ONSET OF CHEMICAL DEPRESSION

637
00:55:26,156 --> 00:55:29,059
TOOK PLACE SHORTLY THEREAFTER,

638
00:55:29,092 --> 00:55:31,061
