643
00:55:44,007 --> 00:55:48,144
FROM A DOCTOR WITH YOUR BACKGROUND AND QUALIFICATIONS.

644
00:55:48,178 --> 00:55:51,815
HOW ARE YOUR SPIRITS, IAN?

645
00:55:51,848 --> 00:55:53,817
MY SPIRITS?

646
00:55:53,850 --> 00:55:56,853
MY SPIRITS.

