666
00:56:46,603 --> 00:56:48,705
WHAT WE'RE ALL ABOUT HERE AT BLACKHURST.

667
00:56:48,738 --> 00:56:50,940
HELL, SHIT, I AM.

668
00:56:52,609 --> 00:56:55,912
YOU'RE A VERY SPECIAL CASE, IAN,

669
00:56:57,847 --> 00:57:00,717
