676
00:57:15,799 --> 00:57:17,901
- BULLSHIT. - THEY ALL DO.

677
00:57:17,934 --> 00:57:19,936
AND YOU'LL SAY NO,

678
00:57:19,969 --> 00:57:22,972
BECAUSE YOU FEEL SO CONFIDENT ABOUT YOURSELF.

679
00:57:23,006 --> 00:57:24,574
AND EVERYONE WILL SAY, OH, GOOD OLD IAN.

680
00:57:24,607 --> 00:57:26,543
HE'S FINALLY CLEANED UP HIS ACT.

681
00:57:26,576 --> 00:57:30,914
